name: (Concept) - Trap/Femboy/Otoko No Ko - 18 Concepts In One
description:
Update - 6/15/23 - Previous '1.5' version got removed for 'Loli' content in the preview images (I'm assuming an unintended side-effect of the flat chests and the use of BasedMix-64) and I couldn't amend the gallery as I got a 404, so I've had to re-upload it with a generic image from the February version.

Maxfield has cleaned the galleries up so it shouldn't happen again, but I'd rather just keep a 'safe' image from the old gallery so it doesn't get nuked again.

NOTE - This is a huge LORA with an experimental optimizer, main issues seem to be tagging is slightly rigid, and there is some loss of detail and color when generating. Reducing LORA weight from 1 to 0.9-0.95 does help with this, so play around with it. I'm mostly interested to see if other people experience similar issues with blur/colors.

New Version - V1.5 Alpha - Alpha version of the LORA. Trained on DAdaptation with over 600 hand-picked images. Supports multiple concepts.

USE TAGS 'Masterpiece, Best Quality' - Fixes the consistency issues with generating and generally increases quality.

Tagging - Each concept has a trigger word, but in general I have not seen this make a huge amount of difference. I would suggest testing concepts with and without these words. 'NSFW' tag seems to be hit or miss and is inconsistent with results:

General tags - Otoko no ko, male focus, 1boy, penis, testicles

All Fours - OTOAF, all fours

Condom - OTOCON, condom on penis, condom (works best without penis/testicle tags but YMMV)

Cowgirl - OTOCOW, cowgirl position, cowgirl, boy on top, sex, anal, yaoi, multiple boys, multiple penises, pov

Doggystyle (kind of works, RNG) - OTODOG, doggystyle, sex from behind, 2boys, yaoi, anal, sex from behind

From Behind - OTOFB, from behind, ass focus, ass

From Below - OTOFBEL, from below

From Side - OTOFSI, from side

Kneeling - OTOKNEE, kneeling

Legs Up - OTOLEU, legs up, ass

Missionary - OTOMISS, missionary, anal, yaoi, sex, 2boys, multiple boys, multiple penises

On Back - OTOOB, on back, spread legs

On Side - OTOOS, on side, ass

On Stomach - OTOONST, on stomach, from behind, ass

Penis in Panties - OTOPIP, penis in panties, bulge (seems to be the strongest tag, recommend always using this)

Penis Under Clothing - Bulge, erection under clothing (this is heavy RNG but I've seen it work)

Sitting - Sitting

Squatting - OTOSQUAT, squatting, from behind, spread legs, facing viewer

Reverse Suspended Congress ( - HEAVY RNG, does not seem to work consistently on some models as it's difficult to generate the male behind the target. YMMV but it will probably work well coupled with another LORA for this position.) - OTOSUS, 2boys, yaoi, sex from behind, reverse suspended congress, anal, faceless male

Good luck.
